Unitron swerves, getting a target lock and firing two missiles at Blue 
Stinger, easily dodging the missiles.

---

Koga Shuko easily dodged Key's shots, firing an optic blast and missile at 
her simultaneously, moving to the left, only a few dozen of the bullets 
digging into his armored side.

---

Anubis rolled to the left, avoiding all but the sonar sohot.  Knocking to his 
butt, though he still fired three optic blasts at Antagony, simultaneously 
firing three plasma blasts at Blue Stinger, and a rocket off at Sona.

---

Hades chuckled, firing two laser bolts at Key, a rocket at Rhinox.
